gomodel:SYNGO_4819  a     owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Figure 1,2: IPs, surface plasmon resonance and crosslinking showed that Noelin1 (OLFM1) interacts directly with GluA2 (GRIA2).\n\nFigure 4: STED imaging in DIV21 cultured hippocampal neurons showed Noelin1 (OLFM1) co-localized with GluA2 (GRIA2) and Homer1 at the PSD.. Experimental description: Figure 4: \"STED imaging in DIV21 cultured hippocampal neurons\"\n\nantibody:\nNoelin1, Neuromab, Clone K96/7" ;
        lego:modelstate   "production" ;
        dc:contributor    "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-2514-0216" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-2286-1587" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-4973-5732" ;
